the flow of milk of a camel, from a heaviness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heaving, of the stomach, or a tendency to vomit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unwillingness to yield a flow of milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8213","headword_ar":"حَصِرٌ","root":"HSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unable to express his mind; to say what he would; to find words to express what he would say;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of shame and confusion of mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accidental"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cause:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSira","text_ar":"حَصِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and one who is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impeded, and unable to proceed, in reading,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recitation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSiyrN","text_ar":"حَصِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoSuwrN","text_ar":"مَحْصُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in both these senses. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Contracted in the bosom; having the bosom contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSiyrN","text_ar":"حَصِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSuwrN","text_ar":"حَصُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) In the Kur iv. 92, some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSirapF Suduwruhumo","text_ar":"حَصِرَةً صُدُورُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their bosoms being contracted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [See 1, latter part.]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Affected with vomiting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Niggardly, tenacious, penurious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avaricious;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSiyrN","text_ar":"حَصِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSuwrN","text_ar":"حَصُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSiyrN","text_ar":"حَصِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who will not drink wine, by reason of niggardliness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSuwrN","text_ar":"حَصُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who will not expend upon those who drink with him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and one who"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of niggardliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"does not take part in the game called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almayosir","text_ar":"المَيْسِر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Suh.) ―         -b5-  Also, (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSirN biAlA^asoraAri","text_ar":"حَصِرٌ بِالاَسْرَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSuwrN","text_ar":"حَصُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone], (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strict concealer of secrets:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a concealer of secrets."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSirapu Al$~axobi","text_ar":"حَصِرَةُ الشَّخْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose flow of milk is suppressed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","S","K","L","A"]},{"entry_id":"n8214","headword_ar":"حُصُرٌ","root":"HSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuSorN","text_ar":"حُصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}